## 4. Spacing Cu

stomization

### Custom Spacing Scale
```javascript
module.exports = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      spacing: {
        // Add custom spacing values
        '128': '32rem',
        '144': '36rem',
        // Pixel values
        '18': '4.5rem',
        '88': '22rem',
        // Percentage values
        '1/10': '10%',
        '9/10': '90%',
      },
    },
  },
}
```

### Override Default Spacing
```javascript
module.exports = {
  theme: {
    spacing: {
      // Completely replace the default spacing scale
      '0': '0',
      '1': '0.25rem',
      '2': '0.5rem',
      '3': '0.75rem',

',
